subject: Do you have a viable project t
body:
Do you have a viable project that is in need of funds injection
We are consultants to an Angel Investors who might be able to help.
We are seeking for individuals who has funds management abilities that can manage
the funds into a profitable investment.
If you have any existing project, we can be able to work with such individuals
Awaiting your prompt response
Regards
Mr Frederick Ying

subject: Re: Do you have a viable project t
body:
Hello Mr. Frederick Ying,

Thank you for reaching out! It's great to hear about your interest in supporting projects that need funding. I'm always eager to learn more about such opportunities.

Could you please share more details about the kind of projects you are interested in? Are there any specific sectors or industries that you prefer?

Also, it would be helpful to know what kind of funds management abilities you're looking for. Do you have any particular expectations or requirements?

Looking forward to hearing from you soon!

Best wishes,
Marilyn
